					<h2 class="blocks--element--title">Our people</h2>
					<p class="blocks--element--text">Our company is all about our people. We have chosen to have a flat hierarchy at Sagacify where everyone is free to speak up, suggest creative approaches and contribute to making solutions. We want our people to develop those skills that are in-line with their interests. Flexibility is at the heart of our work philosophy – you are free to shape your own schedule at Sagacify and get the work done.</p>
					<p class="blocks--element--text">Yes, we work with data, but we place a high value on creativity. Our in-house design team inspire original, inventive thought across the company in all that we do. We use open source tools when possible, contribute to the open source community, and engage in projects that will likely have a positive contribution to society. </p>
					<a href="team" class="btn">Discover the team</a>
				</li>
				<li class="blocks--element blocks--image blocks--greenshadow data-right data-instagram" data-width="15" data-left="23" data-top="1" data-parralax="-1"  data-wow-offset="-500">
