					<p class="blocks--element--text">Sagacify collaborates with Université catholique de Louvain (UCL) and Université libre de Bruxelles (ULB) to stay at the top of academic research within the field of Data Science and help foster the academic field.  We help bridging the gap between academic research and their application in real world solutions.</p>
